ABOUT THIS SKILL

We’re excited to make insurance fun and easy for you.

You don’t need an account to use the Plymouth Rock skill. The skill allows you to get an instant home quote, find a local agent ,and learn about our most popular programs. 

Once you’ve enabled the skill, say “Alexa, open Plymouth Rock…

• Get a quick home quote
• Find an Agent
• Tell me about programs
